---
title: Fajita-Inspired Beyond Meat® Flatbreads with Sour Cream Sauce and Cheddar Cheese
description: We're reimagining family favourite fajitas as a no-fuss flatbread meal! Quick-cooking Beyond Meat® and peppers are seasoned with Tex-Mex paste and nestled atop toasted flatbreads, with gooey cheddar cheese and a drizzle of sour cream sauce to finish!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/fajita-inspired-beyond-meat-flatbreads-3d5b79a8.jpg
